      "explanation": "<p>Correct Answer A - <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"35b089db991692777187f2d1405266\">Epidermolysis</span> bullosa</p>\n<table cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"border-collapse:collapse\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:1px solid black; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:1px solid black; vertical-align:top\">\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><strong>Disease</strong></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:1px solid black; vertical-align:top\">\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><strong>Target antigens</strong></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:1px solid black; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; vertical-align:top\">\n<p style=\"text-align:center\">Bullous pemphigoid</p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; vertical-align:top\">\n<p style=\"text-align:center\">BP 180, BP 230</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:1px solid black; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; vertical-align:top\">\n<p style=\"text-align:center\">Pemphigoid gestationis</p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; vertical-align:top\">\n<p style=\"text-align:center\">BP 180, BP 230</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:1px solid black; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; vertical-align:top\">\n<p style=\"text-align:center\">Linear <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"68bae589ad169277718918627baff4\">IgA</span> bullous <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"cb721815b01692777186acaa47e445\">dermatosis</span> (LABD)</p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; vertical-align:top\">\n<p style=\"text-align:center\">BP 180 (LAD1)</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:1px solid black; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; vertical-align:top\">\n<p style=\"text-align:center\">Epidermolysis bullosa acquisita</p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; vertical-align:top\">\n<p style=\"text-align:center\">Collagen VII</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:1px solid black; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; vertical-align:top\">\n<p style=\"text-align:center\">Bullous <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"ccd536a9071692777191f53538ca30\">lupus</span> erythematosus</p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; vertical-align:top\">\n<p style=\"text-align:center\">Collagen VII</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:1px solid black; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; vertical-align:top\">\n<p style=\"text-align:center\">Cicatricial pemphigoid</p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; vertical-align:top\">\n<p style=\"text-align:center\">BP 180, laminin, \u03b14 and \u03b26 subunits of integrin</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:1px solid black; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; vertical-align:top\">\n<p style=\"text-align:center\">MMP (Mucous <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"34cd707428169277719272942b7905\">Membrane</span> Pemphigoid)</p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; vertical-align:top\">\n<p style=\"text-align:center\">BP 180, <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"73b1d67a501692777191bae0542800\">laminin</span> 332</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:1px solid black; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; vertical-align:top\">\n<p style=\"text-align:center\">Linear IgA</p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; vertical-align:top\">\n<p style=\"text-align:center\">LAD1</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:1px solid black; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; vertical-align:top\">\n<p style=\"text-align:center\">DH (Dermatitis Herpetiformis)</p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; vertical-align:top\">\n<p style=\"text-align:center\">Epidermal <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"4a47b71b801692777200d06df00a08\">Transglutaminase</span> (not from basement membrane)</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n\n\n<p style='font-size: 10px; color: #808080; font-style: italic;'></p>",
